268
00:15:31,666 --> 00:15:35,506
Interesting way to describe
stabbing me in the back.

269
00:15:37,948 --> 00:15:39,746
Come on. We got to
beat him downstairs.

270
00:15:39,746 --> 00:15:42,027
- Same old Jason.
- Only more so.

271
00:15:45,147 --> 00:15:47,468
- Surprise.
- Gotcha.

272
00:15:47,468 --> 00:15:49,108
