305
00:17:42,555 --> 00:17:44,036
Wow.

306
00:17:46,355 --> 00:17:48,116
Congratulations.

307
00:17:49,597 --> 00:17:51,516
Look on the bright side.
If it works out,

308
00:17:51,516 --> 00:17:53,636
