462
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:34,100
The sculptor across the way
beat-up his wife last night.

463
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:36,060
- You're kidding?
- Jason sicked the cops on him.

464
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:38,460
So this isn't just
